            "ratingValue": "1",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "You have money ? Then this school for you. Are you from an affluent family? Then this school is for you.\nDo you have a posh luxury car? Then this school is for you.\n\nYou like to study and make it big? Stay away from this school, ain't gonna make it.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "Symbiosis International School - Clover Park,Viman Nagar"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "tushar ingulkar"
          },
          "datePublished": "2024-05-30",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "1",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I went to Symbiosis school as I am looking for a school to get my daughters admitted in nursery and K.G. respectively.\nDuring my visit to class , I saw that there were no cameras in the class as well as in the lift which is quite surprising. On further inquiry with my friend whose kid is in MYP , she stated that she is looking for another school because education quality is very poor and teacher's behaviour is very bad , teachers only favour few kids and behave differently with others",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "Symbiosis International School - Clover Park,Viman Nagar"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "manjushri nadkarni"
          },
          "datePublished": "2024-05-15",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "1",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "My kid studied here from nursery to class 4th  but several times have come across teachers who favor only a certain class of students (not sure how they identify). Infact once when I raised this concern to the earlier Principal I was told the school is mainly for the affluent class and if I am not happy I may withdraw my child. Nothing has really changed since even with the new head and I have finally changed the school for my kid.\nSo please think about what you are really looking for. If you need a platform to flaunt your status and lure teachers based on this,  then yes this is the school.\nFor people who know the Brahma builders son porsche accident drink n drive case killing two, that's the result of the spoilt brats from schools that are favoring and encouraging the affluent.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
